@startuml State Diagram - Order Lifecycle
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam StateBorderColor #4A90D9
skinparam StateBackgroundColor #EBF4FF
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam StateStartColor #333333
skinparam StateEndColor #333333

title State Diagram — Order Lifecycle

[*] --> PENDING : Customer places order\n(OrderFacade.placeOrder)

PENDING --> CONFIRMED : Payment SUCCESS\n(PaymentService)
PENDING --> CANCELLED : Admin cancels\nor payment FAILED

CONFIRMED --> PREPARING : Tracking step added

PREPARING --> OUT_FOR_DELIVERY : Tracking step added

OUT_FOR_DELIVERY --> DELIVERED : Tracking step added

DELIVERED --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]

PENDING : Entry / Publish OrderStatusChangedEvent
CONFIRMED : Entry / Publish OrderStatusChangedEvent
PREPARING : Entry / Add tracking record
OUT_FOR_DELIVERY : Entry / Add tracking record
DELIVERED : Entry / Customer can review

@enduml
